{
  "_doc": [
    "Source-of-truth de servicios que se construyen como imagen Docker y se",
    "publican a GHCR. Lo consumen:",
    "  - .github/workflows/deploy.yml (matrix dinámica de build).",
    "  - deploy/generate-matrix.sh   (genera la lista 'a desplegar' a partir",
    "    de git diff vs el último commit desplegado).",
    "  - deploy/server/deploy.sh     (pull + up -d en Hetzner, sólo los",
    "    servicios que cambian).",
    "",
    "Reglas:",
    "  - 'paths' debe incluir el directorio propio del servicio + cualquier",
    "    package compartido que use en runtime + pnpm-lock.yaml (cambios al",
    "    lockfile recompilan TODO porque las versiones de los deps cambian).",
    "  - 'restart_policy: rolling' significa que se reinicia con un breve",
    "    downtime aceptable (~5s). Para servicios stateful o críticos usar",
    "    'manual' (el deploy notifica pero no toca el container)."
  ],
  "services": [
    {
      "name": "platform-core",
      "dockerfile": "platform/core/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "platform/core/**",
        "platform/auth/**",
        "platform/notifications/**",
        "platform/payments/**",
        "platform/tenant-config/**",
        "platform/splitpay/**",
        "platform/storage/**",
        "platform/leads/**",
        "platform/donations/**",
        "platform/inquiries/**",
        "platform/verifactu/**",
        "platform/chat/**",
        "platform/tpv/**",
        "platform/commerce/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "platform-marketplace",
      "dockerfile": "platform/marketplace/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "platform/marketplace/**",
        "platform/orders/**",
        "platform/inventory/**",
        "platform/reviews/**",
        "platform/messaging/**",
        "platform/shipping/**",
        "platform/disputes/**",
        "platform/catalog/**",
        "platform/basket/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "platform-restaurant",
      "dockerfile": "platform/restaurant/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "platform/restaurant/**",
        "platform/menu/**",
        "platform/reservations/**",
        "platform/floor-plan/**",
        "platform/kds/**",
        "platform/pos/**",
        "platform/delivery-dispatch/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "platform-appointments",
      "dockerfile": "platform/appointments/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "platform/appointments/**",
        "platform/services/**",
        "platform/resources/**",
        "platform/bookings/**",
        "platform/availability/**",
        "platform/intake-forms/**",
        "platform/telehealth/**",
        "platform/packages/**",
        "platform/practitioner-payouts/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "platform-scheduler",
      "dockerfile": "platform/scheduler/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "platform/scheduler/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "portals",
      "dockerfile": "infra/portals/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "infra/portals/**",
        "apps/portal/**",
        "apps/split-pay/splitpay-portal/**",
        "apps/aikikan/aikikan-portal/**",
        "apps/console/console-portal/**",
        "apps/tenant-console/tenant-console-portal/**",
        "apps/aulavera/aulavera-portal/**",
        "apps/js-electric/js-electric-portal/**",
        "apps/macabeo/macabeo-portal/**",
        "apps/verifactu/verifactu-portal/**",
        "apps/tpv/tpv-portal/**",
        "apps/luciapassardi/luciapassardi-portal/**",
        "packages/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "apps-servers",
      "dockerfile": "apps/apps-servers/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "apps/apps-servers/**",
        "apps/aikikan/aikikan-server/**",
        "apps/aulavera/aulavera-server/**",
        "packages/platform-sdk/**",
        "pnpm-lock.yaml",
        "pnpm-workspace.yaml"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    },
    {
      "name": "nginx",
      "dockerfile": "infra/nginx/Dockerfile",
      "paths": [
        "infra/nginx/**"
      ],
      "restart_policy": "rolling"
    }
  ],
  "infrastructure_notes": [
    "postgres / redis / minio NO se rebuildean — son imágenes upstream con tag",
    "fijado en docker-compose.yml. Si necesitas bumpear postgres a una versión",
    "nueva, hazlo manualmente en producción y documenta el upgrade.",
    "",
    "infra/postgres/init/*.sql se ejecuta SÓLO la primera vez que postgres",
    "arranca con un volumen virgen. En prod nunca se re-ejecuta: cambios al",
    "schema van vía migrations de cada módulo, no por estos scripts."
  ]
}
